              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2026</fr:year>
              <fr:month>7</fr:month>
              <fr:day>19</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:uri>https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00F9/</fr:uri>
            <fr:display-uri>https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00F9/</fr:display-uri>
            <fr:route>/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/sss-00F9/</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Coalgebras as a displayed category">Coalgebras as a displayed category</fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>Fix an endofunctor <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F : \mathcal {C} \to  \mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>. Coalgebras require no
new construction: a coalgebra is an <fr:link href="/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/sss-00F7/" title="Algebras as a displayed category" uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00F7/" display-uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00F7/" type="local">algebra</fr:link> in the opposite
category. Define
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\mathrm {CoalgStr}{\mathopen {}\left (F\right )\mathclose {}} = \mathrm {AlgStr}{\mathopen {}\left (F^{\mathrm {op}}\right )\mathclose {}},]]></fr:tex>
a displayed category over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}^{\mathrm {op}}]]></fr:tex>, where
<fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F^{\mathrm {op}} : \mathcal {C}^{\mathrm {op}} \to  \mathcal {C}^{\mathrm {op}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex> acting on the opposite
category.</html:p>
            <html:p>Concretely, over an object <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex> a displayed object is a structure map
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\gamma  \in  \mathcal {C} {\mathopen {}\left (x , F x\right )\mathclose {}}.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
            <html:p>The category of coalgebras is the opposite of the
<fr:link href="/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FI/" title="Total category" uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FI/" display-uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FI/" type="local">total category</fr:link>:
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\mathrm {Coalg}{\mathopen {}\left (F\right )\mathclose {}} = {\mathopen {}\left (\int  \mathrm {CoalgStr}{\mathopen {}\left (F\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}^{\mathrm {op}}.]]></fr:tex>
The outer opposite returns morphisms to the direction of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>: a
morphism <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (x, \gamma \right )\mathclose {}} \to  {\mathopen {}\left (y, \delta \right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is a map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f : x \to  y]]></fr:tex>
with
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[f \star  \delta  = \gamma  \star  F f.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
